XML tree pretty-printer and supporting styles imported from the WebKit repository:

http://trac.webkit.org/browser/trunk/Source/WebCore/xml/XMLTreeViewer.cpp
http://trac.webkit.org/browser/trunk/Source/WebCore/xml/XMLViewer.css
http://trac.webkit.org/browser/trunk/Source/WebCore/xml/XMLViewer.js
http://trac.webkit.org/browser/trunk/Source/WebCore/css/view-source.css

The WebKit one cannot be invoked directly, since we now display feeds in an iframe, and WebKit's code only triggers in a top frame (see check in XMLTreeViewer::hasNoStyleInformation).
